
# =============================================
# VARIÁVEIS GLOBAIS
# =============================================
@baseUrl = https://projeto-integrador-fiado.onrender.com
@email   = teste@gmail.com
@senha   = 12345


# =============================================
# PASSO 1: Login — o token é capturado automaticamente
# =============================================
# Clique em "Send Request" nesta requisição.
# A variável {{token}} será preenchida sozinha nas próximas.

# @name login
### Login (execute primeiro!)
POST {{baseUrl}}/user/login HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "senha": "{{senha}}"
}

@token = {{login.response.body.$.token}}


# =============================================
# PASSO 2: Rotas protegidas (token automático)
# =============================================

### Criar company
POST {{baseUrl}}/company HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name":     "abracadabra",
  "category": "balas",
  "cnpj":     "12345678000199",
  "places":   "adacy",
  "zip_code": "1356899",
  "addrres":  "rua 2",
  "phone":    "190",
  "userId":   2
}


### Atualizar company
PUT {{baseUrl}}/company/1 HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name":     "teste",
  "category": "Alimentação",
  "cnpj":     "12345678000199",
  "places":   "Localização da empresa",
  "zip_code": "12345-678",
  "addrres":  "Rua Exemplo, 123",
  "phone":    "(11) 1234-5678"
}


### Deletar company
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/company/1 HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


# =============================================
# Rotas públicas (sem token)
# =============================================

### Listar todas as companies
GET {{baseUrl}}/company HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json


### Buscar uma company por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/company/2 HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json


### Buscar por nome
GET {{baseUrl}}/company?name=abrobrinha HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json


### Buscar por tipo
GET {{baseUrl}}/company?type=bo HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json
